data.description: Gorgeous, well maintained home situated at the end of a quiet cul de sac on large 3/4 acre private, flat lot in the highly desirable Cranberry Twp! A beautiful brick front greets you as you enter the home. Gleaming hardwood floors & plush carpet adorn the first floor where you are sure to enjoy the spacious family room with gas fireplace! The kitchen and eat in offer a great view of the enormous back yard, and just off the kitchen is the very conveniently located laundry room and generous pantry. The 2nd floor boasts 4 spacious rooms with ample sized closets in each. The large master bedroom is complete with a true walk in closet and ensuite featuring a soaking tub and brand new separate shower! The basement is fully finished, including a modern electric fireplace adding to the charm and ambiance of the home. Large driveway, accommodates additional 4 vehicles easily. Conveniently located to Rt. 19, I 79, shopping, YMCA, groceries, restaurants, schools, and so much more!
